2018-02-27T18:02:16.000Z","msg":"Too many Chinese people looking for jobs in London and the South East - this push wages down. I remember someone who is from Northern Ireland in this forum said that he manages to earn &pound;4XX per week working as a 打雜 in Northern Ireland."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T18:07:04.000Z","msg":"Have a look at the link below - <br />\n<br />\n#236<br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得就係因為係外國生活無咩活動先容易儲到錢，好似我住北愛既情況，因為無咩學歷只可以去做下外賣檔，但講緊做個打雜都可以有&pound;4xx一個禮拜，中間基本上無咩機會比到黎用錢，儲下儲下就大把錢，去邊度玩都得<br />\n<br />\n不過咁岩自己年紀唔上唔落，又無係呢邊入到大學，識親都個d人唔係大我一個圈就細我一個圈，你叫我點識到女朋友自己開檔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/564236/page/10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/564236/page/10</a>"},{"pid":"72c4d89f8a707febd23014ec491e8841af9dd9eb","tid":567822,"uid":115484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"412449615c13c52812ed345760e529a29746f8b3","tid":567822,"uid":2329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T18:04:52.000Z","msg":"去完兩年返黎，遊左大半個歐洲<br />\n大半時間有工開，第二年撈返香港做開既專業工，一生無憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 特區就等抽左sponsor 先啦，好似三四月有一輪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T18:11:43.000Z","msg":"好似三四月有一輪 - there are only two rounds of Certificate of Sponsorship (CoS) applications per year. The main round for 2018 has started and applications will close on 5 March 2018.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.whs.gov.hk/en/partners.php?location=uk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.whs.gov.hk%2Fen%2Fpartners.php%3Flocation%3Duk&d=Px4FN%2BDPswkdiCZyJZdSqYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=0382578a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.whs.gov.hk/en/partners.php?location=uk</a><br />\n<br />\nIf you managed to get a CoS this time round, it is valid until 9 July 2018.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.whs.gov.hk/en/partners.php?location=uk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.whs.gov.hk%2Fen%2Fpartners.php%3Flocation%3Duk&d=Px4FN%2BDPswkdiCZyJZdSqYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=0382578a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.whs.gov.hk/en/partners.php?location=uk</a>"},{"pid":"4a660ce7eadb9cc96dd012c32fee871100a15c4c","tid":567822,"uid":170704,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T21:20:48.000Z","msg":"點解會見到自己係另一個帖post既野 😂<br />\n<br />\nBTW,黎得呢邊working holiday 既話都係餐飲業多<br />\n<br />\n不過以前識得一個去左做整麵包既工廠"},{"pid":"8afdead5e2a2f4a9213238231029b77368955357","tid":567822,"uid":28052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T22:57:34.000Z","msg":"多數waiter waitress架啦"},{"pid":"1df7f81cd8d1dc309cf4566b74382c116d5f1360","tid":567822,"uid":169807,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T23:09:22.000Z","msg":"其實樓主連點申請working holiday 都要問人唔識google<br />\n你覺得你真係適合去英國working holiday 咩"},{"pid":"70cb5da41fca67d71a103c04396fb0ddc6e88128","tid":567822,"uid":170611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1422eb9fec21e73a10b2f448393987c4714d077f","tid":567822,"uid":148532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T07:57:54.000Z","msg":"本人想申請今年英國working holiday想問應該係邊到入手？<br />\n上網睇資料好多有啲亂，唔太明點搞個visa。<br />\n求各位幫幫手教教我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T00:33:15.000Z","msg":"想問working holiday 要點申請"},{"pid":"40d17e3735590d1d9491ff4b8aca42705470af7f","tid":567822,"uid":148532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a660ce7eadb9cc96dd012c32fee871100a15c4c","tid":567822,"uid":170704,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T21:20:48.000Z","msg":"點解會見到自己係另一個帖post既野 😂<br />\n<br />\nBTW,黎得呢邊working holiday 既話都係餐飲業多<br />\n<br />\n不過以前識得一個去左做整麵包既工廠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:44:48.000Z","msg":"麵包工廠好似唔錯"},{"pid":"ba2c1601f1ecc093ccb82c14778c115e97502d89","tid":567822,"uid":148532,"like":0,"dislike":0